              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

              <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-photo">
            <img src={`${base}/img/team/armin.jpg`} alt="Armin Briegel" />
          </div>
          <div class="team-info">
            <h3>Armin Briegel</h3>
            <span class="team-role">Scripting OS X, MacAdmins.news</span>
            <p class="team-bio">
Armin Briegel is a highly respected consultant and author in the Mac administration community, best known for his blog Scripting OS X (scriptingosx.com) and his extensive work with Apple device management. He has been managing Macs and their users for nearly 30 years and has held virtually every technical job title in the Apple ecosystem.
            </p>
