            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Additional Team Member -->
      <div class="team-grid team-grid-single">
        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-photo">
            <img src={`${base}/img/team/jordy.jpg`} alt="Jordy Thery">
          </div>
          <div class="team-info">
            <h3>Jordy Thery</h3>
            <span class="team-role">Social Media Fellow</span>
            <p class="team-bio">
Is a Belgian tech nerd with a deep passion for Apple. Working for Belgiums largest Apple Premium Partner he tries to evangelise the use of Apple devices in Enterprise and being active within the MacAdmins community whilst he does it.</p>
            <div class="team-links">
              <a href="https://macadmins.slack.com/team/U04AHQ0F5FT" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Slack" class="team-link">
