            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Community Thank You Box -->
      <div class="ambassadors-content text-center">
        <h2 class="ambassadors-title">Community Ambassadors</h2>
        <p class="ambassadors-message">
          Mac Admins Europe wouldn't be possible without the countless volunteers, advocates, and community members
          who work tirelessly behind the scenes. From organizing local meetups and spreading the word,
          to providing feedback and helping newcomers feel welcome — your contributions make this community what it is.
        </p>
        <p class="ambassadors-message">
          To everyone who has shared their knowledge, mentored others, or simply shown up to support fellow admins:
        </p>
        <h3 class="ambassadors-thanks">Thank you!</h3>
        <p class="ambassadors-message ambassadors-final">
          This event is for the community, by the community — and that means all of you.
        </p>
      </div>
